title: About Me
text:
Hello, my name is Max Lubelczyk, and I am a Senior at the University of New Hampshire, studying sustainability and agricultural food systems with an emphasis in marketing agricultural technology. I will be graduating in December, and will be moving to North Carolina in January.
Thanks for checking out my web site!
